\chapter{Errata}
\section{Chapter 2}
\begin{description}

\item[p.18] Bottom: the Feynman rules for outgoing fermions should of course have bars on the $u_{+/-}$ in the gray box. Somehow those got erased in the editorial process, booo! 

\item[p.26] Exercise 2.10(c). Missing subscripts $a\dot{b}$ on the RHS of the expression for the polarization. 
(Reyimuaji Yakefu 8/22/2016)

\item[p.27] Equation (2.55). Missing minus after the last equality. So it should read 
\[... = - \left<13\right>[3q]\] 
(Filipe Rudrigues 3/23/2015)

\item[p.31] Equation (2.67): index mistake - last term should have index structure $A^\mu A^\nu A_\mu A_\nu$. (João Caldeira 4/27/2016) 

\item[p.31] Equation (2.72): $f^{12b} f^{b34}  =  - Tr(1234) + Tr(1243) + Tr(1342) - Tr(1432)$.
(Steve Naculich and Anatoliy Dovbnya 7/23/2016)

\item[p.33] Second line, second equation should be $[q_2 3] <13> = - [q_2 2] <12>$. 
(João Caldeira 4/27/2016) 

\item[p.36] Equation (2.92) and line below: $A_4(...)$ should be $A_4[...]$ to properly indicate that these are color-ordered amplitudes (three instances). Also, note inconsistency about factors of $g^2$ between (2.73), (2.91), and (2.92).
(Reyimuaji Yakefu 8/22/2016)

\end{description}

